title: Andre Rieu - Life Is Beutiful - 2000 Gala Millennium Concert
description:
Violinist Andre Rieu and his orchestra perform a program of light classical favorites and beloved pop tunes in this concert video, recorded in the idyllic setting of the Waldbuhne Amphitheater, a beautiful open-air amphitheater in Berlin surrounded by gardens.
